"{\n  \"text\": \"The life web all around us is dominated by very, very small creatures. Bacteria, acacia, and all these other very small organisms that work basically consuming the calories of the world. You work in the same way. And you need to eat and ingest other bacteria to get this life web within you working at its maximum potential. Raw fruits and vegetables and partially cooked meats are the way to get the living elements back in you to reinforce your living element, which is your gut bacteria. You are host to this wonderful element that digests your food, that processes the world into calories, and you can have energy. This is your fundamental action. And without a healthy gut bacteria, you are going to be suffering. There is no health if your gut is in there. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" The life web all around us is dominated by very, very small creatures.\",\n      \"start\": 0.32,\n      \"end\": 5.28,\n      \"duration\": 4.96,\n      \"confidence\": 0.989,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" The\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" li\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"fe\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" web\",\n          \"start\": 1.12,\n          \"end\": 1.44,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" all\",\n          \"start\": 1.68,\n          \"end\": 1.92,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" a\",\n          \"start\": 1.92,\n          \"end\": 2.0,\n       